OL,3,C'You should never come that close to
OL,4,Cdeath': Louise Thompson recalls son's
OL,5,Cbirth
OL,7,FSpeaking to ITV News, the reality TV
OL,8,Fstar discusses the aftermath of her
OL,9,Fson's birth that left her with PTSD
OL,11,FLouise Thompson and I both welcomed
OL,12,Four first baby boys in November 2021,
OL,13,Ffour days apart. Both of us were told
OL,14,Fthat as fit and healthy women we would
OL,15,Fbe ideal candidates for home-births.
OL,16,FWe both ended up having .
OL,18,FSharing has, for a long time, helped
OL,19,Fmany women to process and understand
OL,20,Fthe life-changing event they have
OL,21,Fexperienced.
