OL,3,C'You should never come that close to
OL,4,Cdeath': Louise Thompson recalls son's
OL,5,Cbirth
OL,7,FAs a former reality TV star, Louise,
OL,8,Fof Made in Chelsea fame, is used to
OL,9,Fsharing huge parts of her life with
OL,10,Fher one million Instagram followers,
OL,11,Fbut the story of her son's arrival is
OL,12,Fone she'd rather not have to re-live.
OL,14,FAfter suffering complications, Louise
OL,15,Fendured a three-hour operation and
OL,16,Flost more than three litres of blood.
OL,18,FShe had always wanted an elective
OL,19,Fcaesarean section but was persuaded by
OL,20,Fmedics not to.
