OL,4,Cdeath': Louise Thompson recalls son's
OL,5,Cbirth
OL,7,F"I just felt like no one wanted to
OL,8,Flisten" she told me.
OL,10,FLouise had predicted she might die
OL,11,Fduring childbirth journaling in the
OL,12,Fdays before her birth. She was told
OL,13,Fwhat happened to her in a birth
OL,14,Fdebrief with the hospital.
