OL,3,C'You should never come that close to
OL,4,Cdeath': Louise Thompson recalls son's
OL,5,Cbirth
OL,7,FLast week, Louise shared her story at
OL,8,Fa parliamentary inquiry into birth
OL,9,Ftrauma and heard "harrowing" evidence
OL,10,Ffrom thousands of women. The all-party
OL,11,Finquiry, led by Conservative MP Theo
OL,12,FClarke and Labour MP Rosie Duffield,
OL,13,Ffound "poor care is all frequently
OL,14,Ftolerated as normal, and women are
OL,15,Ftreated as an inconvenience".
OL,17,F"You should never have to come that
OL,18,Fclose to death to then survive. It
OL,19,Fcompletely destroyed my life. I didn't
OL,20,Fknow how to cope with that level of
OL,21,Ffear," Louise said.
