OL,3,C'You should never come that close to
OL,4,Cdeath': Louise Thompson recalls son's
OL,5,Cbirth
OL,7,FIn April, Louise announced on social
OL,8,Fmedia she had been through further
OL,9,Fsurgery to have part of her bowel
OL,10,Fremoved after struggling with
OL,11,Fulcerative colitis for six years. She
OL,12,Fbelieves the medication she has been
OL,13,Ftaking since the birth of her son may
OL,14,Fhave contributed to her condition
OL,15,Fworsening.
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G     G8/12
