OL,7,FA spokesperson for Chelsea and
OL,8,FWestminster Hospital NHS Foundation
OL,9,FTrust said: "The health and wellbeing
OL,10,Fof those in our care is our absolute
OL,11,Fpriority, and it's right we recognise
OL,12,Fwhen this care doesn't meet the
OL,13,Fstandards that patients rightly expect
OL,14,Fand that we learn from it.
OL,16,F"Patient safety and the quality of
OL,17,Fcare we provide are fundamental to our
OL,18,Fmaternity service.
